 inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">· Good analytical and organizational skills</p><p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">· Sense of responsibility and ability to take initiatives and work independently.</p><p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">· Willingness of self-education in ICT-related fields.</p><p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">· Excellent communication and interpersonal skills.</p><p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">· Flexibility and resistance to stress.</p><p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">· Be able to travel within Syria.</p><p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">· Able to write clear and concise reports, procedures, and quality documents.</p><p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\" font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(255, 0, 0)\"><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">PS: Syrian Arab Red Crescent Does Not Provide Any Transportations For Employees.</strong></span></p>\r\n<br /></p>', 'en', 21),
(19, 'عن منظمة الهلال الأحمر العربي السوري', '<p>منظمة الهلال الأحمر العربي السوري، منظمة إنسانية تتمتع بالاستقلال المالي والإداري ذات شخصية اعتبارية، مهمّتها الاستجابة بالوقت المناسب وبشكل فعّال، لمساعدة الأشخاص المتضررين والحفاظ على كرامتهم،<br />&nbsp;وبناء قدرتهم على الصمود والتكيّف مع آثار الأزمات وحالات الطوارئ، والتعافي منها، من خلال شبكة قوية من الموظفين والمتطوعين المؤهلين، وشراكات فعّالة داخل وخارج الحركة الدولية للصليب الأحمر والهلال الأحمر، ووفقاً للمبادئ الأساسية السبعة للحركة.<br /></p>', 'ar', 1),
(20, 'About SARC', '<p>The Syrian Arab Red Crescent is a humanitarian organization with financial and administrative independence and a legal personality.<br />Its mission is to respond effectively and promptly to help affected people, preserve human dignity, build their resilience and ability to adapt to the effects of crises and emergencies, and facilitate recovery, through a strong network of qualified staff and volunteers, and effective partnerships inside and outside the International Red Cross and Red Crescent Movement, and in accordance with the seven fundamental principles of the Movement.<br /></p>', 'en', 1),
(21, 'مبادئ منظمة الهلال الأحمر العربي السوري', '<p><p dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;direction:rtl;unicode-bidi:\r\nembed\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">توجه عملنا مبادئ أساسية سبعة، وتشكل إطاراً\r\nأخلاقياً وتنفيذياً له، وتقع في صميم أنشطتنا الإنسانية، وهي قاسم مشترك يوحّد\r\nمكونات الحركة الدولية، وهي<span style=\"font-style: italic;\"> اللجنة الدولية للصليب الأحمر</span>، و<span style=\"font-style: italic;\">الجمعيات الوطنية\r\nللصليب الأحمر والهلال الأحمر</span>، و<span style=\"font-style: italic;\">الاتحاد الدولي</span> <span style=\"font-style: italic;\">لجمعيات الصليب الأحمر والهلال\r\nالأحمر</span>.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;direction:rtl;unicode-bidi:\r\nembed\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\">الإنسانية</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;direction:rtl;unicode-bidi:\r\nembed\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">نضع مبدأ الإنسانية في المقام الأول أكثر من أي\r\nشيء آخر، وهو يعكس الحاجة إلى العمل من أجل منع المعاناة الإنسانية وتخفيفها، واحترام\r\nكرامة الإنسان ومساعدة الناس، بغض النظر عن من هم وأين هم، ويشكّل ذلك أمراً بالغ\r\nالأهمية في كل ما نقوم به.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;direction:rtl;unicode-bidi:\r\nembed\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\">عدم التحيّز</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;direction:rtl;unicode-bidi:\r\nembed\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">لا نميّز في أنشطتنا، بين الأشخاص على أساس\r\nجنسياتهم أو عرقهم أو معتقداتهم الدينية أو طبقتهم الاجتماعية أو آرائهم السياسية،\r\nفكل ما نسعى إليه هو التخفيف من معاناة هؤلاء الأشخاص، مسترشدين بمعيار واحد هو\r\nمدى احتياجاتهم، مع إعطاء الأولوية لأشد حالات المعاناة إلحاحاً.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;direction:rtl;unicode-bidi:\r\nembed\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\">الحياد</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;direction:rtl;unicode-bidi:\r\nembed\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">لا ننحاز إلى أي طرف في الأعمال العدائية أو نتدخل\r\nفي أي وقت في خلافات ذات طبيعة سياسية، أو عرقية أو دينية أو أيديولوجية، بما يضمن\r\nثقة الجميع في الحركة وقدرتها على تقديم الدعم الإنساني للجميع</span><span dir=\"LTR\">.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;direction:rtl;unicode-bidi:\r\nembed\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;direction:rtl;unicode-bidi:\r\nembed\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\">الاستقلال</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:right;direction:rtl;unicode-bidi:\r\nembed\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">مبدأ الاستقلال يعني أنّ الحركة يجب أن تقاوم\r\nأي تدخل يحرفها عن تجسيد مبادئ الإنسانية وعدم التحيّز والحياد، ورغم أن الجمعيات\r\nالوطنية، تعمل كجهات مساعدة في الخدمات الإنسانية التي تقدّمها حكوماتها وتخضع\r\nلقوانين بلدانها، إلاّ أنّها تحافظ دائماً على استقلالها الذاتي حتى تتمكّن في\r\nجميع الأوقات من العمل وفقاً لمبادئ الحركة.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;direction:rtl;unicode-bidi:\r\nembed\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\">الخدمة التطوعية</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:right;direction:rtl;unicode-bidi:\r\nembed\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">يجسّد مبدأ الخدمة التطوعية دافع مشترك يوحّد\r\nجميع العاملين داخل الحركة، وهو الرغبة في مساعدة الآخرين، فهو مصدر إلهام وإعلان\r\nعن التضامن في الوقت نفسه، وسواء كان الأعضاء يتطوعون دون أجر، أو لقاء شكل من\r\nأشكال التقدير أو حتى مكافأة متواضعة، فهم يفعلون ذلك ليس بدافع تحقيق مكاسب\r\nمالية، ولكن من خلال الالتزام الفردي والتفاني في تحقيق الهدف السامي للإنسانية.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;direction:rtl;unicode-bidi:\r\nembed\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\">الوحدة</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;direction:rtl;unicode-bidi:\r\nembed\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">لا يمكن أن توجد سوى جمعية واحدة للصليب الأحمر\r\nأو الهلال الأحمر في البلد الواحد، ويجب أن تكون مفتوحة للجميع، وأن تضطلع\r\nبأنشطتها الإنسانية في جميع أراضي ذلك البلد</span><span dir=\"LTRL\">.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;direction:rtl;unicode-bidi:\r\nembed\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\">العالمية</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;direction:rtl;unicode-bidi:\r\nembed\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">الحركة هيئة عالمية، وتحظى كل الجمعيات الوطنية\r\nفيها بمكانة متساوية وتقع على عاتقها المسؤوليات والواجبات ذاتها في مؤازرة بعضها\r\nبعضاً.</span></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<br /></p>\r\n<style>\r\n /* Style Definitions */\r\n table.MsoNormalTable\r\n	{mso-style-name:\"Table Normal\";\r\n	mso-tstyle-rowband-size:0;\r\n	mso-tstyle-colband-size:0;\r\n	mso-style-noshow:yes;\r\n	mso-style-priority:99;\r\n	mso-style-parent:\"\";\r\n	mso-padding-alt:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\r\n	mso-para-margin-top:0cm;\r\n	mso-para-margin-right:0cm;\r\n	mso-para-margin-bottom:8.0pt;\r\n	mso-para-margin-left:0cm;\r\n	line-height:107%;\r\n	mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\r\n	font-size:11.0pt;\r\n	font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif;\r\n	mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\n	mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\n	mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\n	mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\n	mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\n	mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;}\r\n</style>', 'ar', 3);
INSERT INTO `section_details` (`id`, `title`, `content`, `lang`, `section_id`) VALUES
(22, 'The Fundamental Principles', '<p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\" />\r\n<meta name=\"ProgId\" content=\"Word.DocumentW\" />\r\n<meta name=\"Generator\" content=\"Microsoft Word 15\" />\r\n<meta name=\"Originator\" content=\"Microsoft Word 15\" />\r\n<link rel=\"File-List\r\n\" href=\"file:///C:/Users/ASUS/AppData/Local/Packages/oice_16_974fa576_32c1d314_e43/AC/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_filelist.xml\" />\r\n<xml>\r\n \r\n  \r\n \r\n</xml>\r\n<link rel=\"themeData\r\n\" href=\"file:///C:/Users/ASUS/AppData/Local/Packages/oice_16_974fa576_32c1d314_e43/AC/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_themedata.thmx\" />\r\n<link rel=\"colorSchemeMapping\r\n\" href=\"file:///C:/Users/ASUS/AppData/Local/Packages/oice_16_974fa576_32c1d314_e43/AC/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_colorschememapping.xml\" />\r\n<xml>\r\n \r\n  </xml><p class=\"MsoNormalM\"><span>Humanity, impartiality, neutrality, independence, voluntary service,\r\nunity, and universality: these seven Fundamental Principles sum up the\r\nMovement’s ethics and are at the core of its approach to helping people in need\r\nduring armed conflict, natural disasters, and other emergencies.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormalM\"><span>The Fundamental Principles are key to the Movement’s identity. Adherence\r\nto these principles ensures the humanitarian nature of the Movement’s work and\r\nbrings consistency to the broad range of activities it undertakes around the\r\nworld. The principles provide a common bond for the National Societies, which\r\nvary greatly in structure, culture, and membership.</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><br />\r\n</span><span><br /><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">HUMANITY</span></span><br />\r\nThe International Red Cross and Red Crescent Movement, born of a desire to\r\nbring assistance without discrimination to the wounded on the battlefield,\r\nendeavors – in its international and national capacities – to prevent and\r\nalleviate suffering wherever it may be found. Its purpose is to protect life\r\nand health and to ensure respect for every human being. It promotes mutual\r\nunderstanding, friendship, cooperation, and lasting peace among all peoples.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormalM\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormalM\"><span><span style=\"font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\">IMPARTIALITY</span><br />\r\nThe Movement does not discriminate as to nationality, race, religious\r\nbeliefs, class, or political opinions. It endeavors to relieve the suffering of\r\nindividuals, being guided solely by their needs, and to give priority to the\r\nmost urgent cases of distress.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormalM\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormalM\"><span><span style=\"font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\">NEUTRALITY</span><br />\r\nTo continue to enjoy the confidence of all, the Movement may not take\r\nsides in hostilities or engage at any time in controversies of a political,\r\nracial, religious or ideological nature.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormalM\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormalM\"><span><span style=\"font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\">INDEPENDENCE</span><br />\r\nThe Movement is independent. The National Societies, while auxiliaries in the\r\nhumanitarian services of their governments and subject to the laws of their\r\nrespective countries, must always maintain their autonomy so that they may be\r\nable at all times to act following the principles of the Movement.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormalM\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormalM\"><span><span style=\"font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\">VOLUNTARY SERVICE<br /></span>\r\nThe Movement is a voluntary relief movement not prompted in any manner by a desire for gain.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormalM\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<br /></p>', 'en', 3),
(23, 'قصتنا', '<p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\" />\r\n<meta name=\"ProgId\" content=\"Word.DocumentW\" />\r\n<meta name=\"Generator\" content=\"Microsoft Word 15\" />\r\n<meta name=\"Originator\" content=\"Microsoft Word 15\" />\r\n<link rel=\"File-List\r\n\" href=\"file:///C:/Users/ASUS/AppData/Local/Packages/oice_16_974fa576_32c1d314_e43/AC/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_filelist.xml\" />\r\n<xml>\r\n \r\n  \r\n \r\n</xml>\r\n<link rel=\"themeData\r\n\" href=\"file:///C:/Users/ASUS/AppData/Local/Packages/oice_16_974fa576_32c1d314_e43/AC/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_themedata.thmx\" />\r\n<link rel=\"colorSchemeMapping\r\n\" href=\"file:///C:/Users/ASUS/AppData/Local/Packages/oice_16_974fa576_32c1d314_e43/AC/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_colorschememapping.xml\" />\r\n<xml>\r\n \r\n  </xml><p dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;direction:rtl;unicode-bidi:\r\nembed\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">في عام 1942\r\nشكّل خيرة مثقفي دمشق، النواة الأولى لتأسيس منظمة<span style=\"font-style: italic;\"> الهلال الأحمر العربي السوري</span>،\r\nبهدف تقديم خدمات إنسانية في السلم والحرب، وفي عام 1946 حصلت المنظمة على اعتراف عالمي،\r\nمن<span style=\"font-style: italic;\"> اللجنة الدولية للصليب الأحمر</span>، وخلال أقل من نصف قرن، كبرت عائلتها وتوزعت على\r\nامتداد المحافظات، </span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">وأصبحت عضواً في الحركة الدولية والاتحاد\r\nالدولي لجمعيات الصليب الأحمر والهلال الأحمر في جنيف، والأمانة العامة لجمعيات\r\nالهلال الأحمر والصليب الأحمر العربية.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;direction:rtl;unicode-bidi:\r\nembed\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">أولى استجابات\r\nالمنظمة، كانت عام 1945، إثر العدوان الفرنسي على دمشق، حيث استجاب المتطوعون وكان\r\nعددهم قليلاً جداً، وبسيارة إسعاف واحدة، لأكثر من 1800 حالة إسعافية، وأصيب\r\nواستشهد حينها الطبيب المسعف مسلم البارودي، ليكون أول شهداء المنظمة.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;direction:rtl;unicode-bidi:\r\nembed\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">ومع مرور\r\nالسنوات، توالت استجابات </span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">الهلال الأحمر العربي السوري </span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">دولياً، </span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">في\r\nالعراق، وألمانيا، ومصر، وفلسطين، وإيران، وإندونيسيا</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">، ومحلياً لنازحي الجولان ومتضرري حرب تشرين،&nbsp;وانهيار\r\nسد زيزون، كما لبى </span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">احتياجات الوافدين واللاجئين من فلسطين\r\nولبنان والعراق</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"> إلى\r\nسوريا.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;direction:rtl;unicode-bidi:\r\nembed\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">وفي عام 2011، </span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">بدأت الأزمة السورية، ومعها أكبر استجابة في تاريخ الهلال الأحمر\r\nالعربي السوري</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">، توسعت\r\nخلالها البرامج والخدمات لتلبية كل احتياج، وتخفيف معاناة المتضررين والأشد ضعفاً،\r\nوتأمين الحماية لهم وحفظ كرامتهم، ومساعدتهم على التعافي، ليكون </span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">الفاعل الإنساني الرائد في سوريا.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;direction:rtl;unicode-bidi:\r\nembed\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">ويستمر الهلال الأحمر العربي السوري بدوره\r\nالفريد، ملتزماً بمبادئه الإنسانية، والمصداقية والثقة اللتين يتمتع بهما في\r\nالمجتمع، عبر استجابته الدائمة والفورية، لحالات الطوارئ والأزمات والكوارث. </span></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<br /></p>', 'ar', 2),
(24, 'Our Story', '<p><br /><p class=\"MsoNormalM\">In 1942, prominent doctors, lawyers, and social workers in Damascus\r\nformed the nucleus of the<span style=\"font-style: italic;\"> Syrian Arab Red Crescent</span>, to provide humanitarian assistance in both peacetime and wartime. In 1946, the\r\norganization received international recognition from the International\r\nCommittee of the Red Cross. Over the next several decades, the Syrian Arab Red\r\nCrescent expanded its reach across the country, joining the <span style=\"font-style: italic;\">International\r\nFederation of Red Cross and Red Crescent Societies </span>and the General Secretariat\r\nof the Arab Red Crescent and Red Cross Societies.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormalM\"><span>The organization\'s first major response came in 1945, following the\r\nFrench aggression on Damascus. Despite limited resources, volunteers responded\r\nto over 1,800 emergency cases with a single ambulance. Tragically, paramedic\r\nMuslim Al-Baroudi was injured and lost his life during this response, becoming\r\nthe organization\'s first martyr.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormalM\"><span>Throughout its history, the Syrian Arab Red Crescent has provided\r\ninternational assistance, including medical aid to earthquake victims in Iran\r\nand support to refugees in Palestine, Lebanon, and Iraq.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormalM\"><span>The Syrian crisis, which began in 2011, presented the organization with\r\nits greatest challenge. The Syrian Arab Red Crescent scaled up its operations\r\nsignificantly, expanding programs to meet the diverse needs of millions of\r\naffected people.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormalM\"><span>The organization continues to play a vital role in Syria, adhering to\r\nits humanitarian principles and maintaining the trust of the Syrian people. It\r\nremains committed to providing immediate and effective assistance during\r\nemergencies and crises.</span></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<br /></p>\r\n<style>\r\n\r\n</style>\r\n<style>\r\n /* Style Definitions */\r\n table.MsoNormalTable\r\n	{mso-style-name:\"Table Normal\";\r\n	mso-tstyle-rowband-size:0;\r\n	mso-tstyle-colband-size:0;\r\n	mso-style-noshow:yes;\r\n	mso-style-priority:99;\r\n	mso-style-parent:\"\";\r\n	mso-padding-alt:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\r\n	mso-para-margin-top:0cm;\r\n	mso-para-margin-right:0cm;\r\n	mso-para-margin-bottom:8.0pt;\r\n	mso-para-margin-left:0cm;\r\n	line-height:107%;\r\n	mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\r\n	font-size:11.0pt;\r\n	font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif;\r\n	mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\n	mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\n	mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\n	mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\n	mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\n	mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;}\r\n</style>', 'en', 2),
(25, 'أين نعمل؟', '<p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\" />\r\n<meta name=\"ProgId\" content=\"Word.DocumentW\" />\r\n<meta name=\"Generator\" content=\"Microsoft Word 15\" />\r\n<meta name=\"Originator\" content=\"Microsoft Word 15\" />\r\n<link rel=\"File-List\r\n\" href=\"file:///C:/Users/ASUS/AppData/Local/Packages/oice_16_974fa576_32c1d314_e43/AC/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_filelist.xml\" />\r\n<xml>\r\n \r\n  \r\n \r\n</xml>\r\n<link rel=\"themeData\r\n\" href=\"file:///C:/Users/ASUS/AppData/Local/Packages/oice_16_974fa576_32c1d314_e43/AC/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_themedata.thmx\" />\r\n<link rel=\"colorSchemeMapping\r\n\" href=\"file:///C:/Users/ASUS/AppData/Local/Packages/oice_16_974fa576_32c1d314_e43/AC/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_colorschememapping.xml\" />\r\n<xml>\r\n \r\n  </xml><p dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;direction:rtl;unicode-bidi:\r\nembed\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">تعمل منظمة<span style=\"font-style: italic;\"> الهلال الأحمر العربي السوري</span> على\r\nامتداد سوريا، في كل مكان يحتاجها، عبر أكثر من 15700 متطوعاً وموظفاً، ومقرها\r\nالأساسي في<span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"> دمشق،</span> ولديها 14 فرعاً في جميع المحافظات، و64 شعبة تابعة للفروع نشطة.</span></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<br /></p>', 'ar', 4),
(26, 'Our Location', '<p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\" />\r\n<meta name=\"ProgId\" content=\"Word.DocumentW\" />\r\n<meta name=\"Generator\" content=\"Microsoft Word 15\" />\r\n<meta name=\"Originator\" content=\"Microsoft Word 15\" />\r\n<link rel=\"File-List\r\n\" href=\"file:///C:/Users/ASUS/AppData/Local/Packages/oice_16_974fa576_32c1d314_e43/AC/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_filelist.xml\" />\r\n<xml>\r\n \r\n  \r\n \r\n</xml>\r\n<link rel=\"themeData\r\n\" href=\"file:///C:/Users/ASUS/AppData/Local/Packages/oice_16_974fa576_32c1d314_e43/AC/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_themedata.thmx\" />\r\n<link rel=\"colorSchemeMapping\r\n\" href=\"file:///C:/Users/ASUS/AppData/Local/Packages/oice_16_974fa576_32c1d314_e43/AC/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_colorschememapping.xml\" />\r\n<xml>\r\n \r\n  </xml><p class=\"MsoNormalM\">The<span style=\"font-style: italic;\"> Syrian Arab Red Crescent</span> works across <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Syria</span>, wherever it is needed,\r\nthrough more than 15,700 volunteers and employees. Its headquarters is in\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Damascus</span>, and it has 14 branches in all governorates and 64 active offices\r\naffiliated with the branches.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<br /></p>', 'en', 4),
(27, 'عن الحركة الدولية للصليب الأحمر والهلال الأحمر', '<p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\" />\r\n<meta name=\"ProgId\" content=\"Word.DocumentW\" />\r\n<meta name=\"Generator\" content=\"Microsoft Word 15\" />\r\n<meta name=\"Originator\" content=\"Microsoft Word 15\" />\r\n<link rel=\"File-List\r\n\" href=\"file:///C:/Users/ASUS/AppData/Local/Packages/oice_16_974fa576_32c1d314_e43/AC/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_filelist.xml\" />\r\n<xml>\r\n \r\n  \r\n \r\n</xml>\r\n<link rel=\"themeData\r\n\" href=\"file:///C:/Users/ASUS/AppData/Local/Packages/oice_16_974fa576_32c1d314_e43/AC/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_themedata.thmx\" />\r\n<link rel=\"colorSchemeMapping\r\n\" href=\"file:///C:/Users/ASUS/AppData/Local/Packages/oice_16_974fa576_32c1d314_e43/AC/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_colorschememapping.xml\" />\r\n<xml>\r\n \r\n  </xml><p dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align:justify;direction:rtl;unicode-bidi:\r\nembed\"><br /></p><p dir=\"RTL\" style=\"margin-bottom:18.0pt;text-align:right;background:white;direction:rtl;unicode-bidi:\r\nembed\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:#262626\">أكبر\r\nشبكة إنسانية عالمية، تتألف من اللجنة الدولية للصليب الأحمر، و191 جمعية وطنية\r\nللصليب الأحمر والهلال الأحمر، والاتحاد الدولي لجمعيات الصليب الأحمر والهلال\r\nالأحمر، يوحّدها هدف مركزي، هو مساعدة أولئك الذين يعانون من دون تمييز وبالتالي\r\nالمساهمة في تحقيق السلام في العالم.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"RTL\" style=\"margin-bottom:18.0pt;text-align:right;background:white;direction:rtl;unicode-bidi:\r\nembed\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:#262626\">والرموز\r\nالمميزة للحركة، هي شارتا الصليب الأحمر والهلال الأحمر، وهي بمثابة رموز للحماية\r\nوالتعبير عن الحياد، وتتيح هاتان الشارتان للعاملين في المجال الإنساني العمل\r\nبأمان في مناطق النزاع، بما يكفل إيصال المساعدات الحيوية لمن هم في أمس الحاجة\r\nإليها، وإلى جانب شارتي الصليب الأحمر والهلال الأحمر، اعتُمدت شارة الكريستالة\r\nالحمراء عام 2005 لتناسب البلدان التي لا تستخدم أيّاً من الرمزين الآخرين لأسباب\r\nثقافية أو سياسية</span><span dir=\"LTR\r\n\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:#262626\">.</span></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<br /></p>', 'ar', 5),
(28, 'About The International Red Cross and Red Crescent Movement', '<p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\" />\r\n<meta name=\"ProgId\" content=\"Word.DocumentW\" />\r\n<meta name=\"Generator\" content=\"Microsoft Word 15\" />\r\n<meta name=\"Originator\" content=\"Microsoft Word 15\" />\r\n<link rel=\"File-List\r\n\" href=\"file:///C:/Users/ASUS/AppData/Local/Packages/oice_16_974fa576_32c1d314_e43/AC/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_filelist.xml\" />\r\n<xml>\r\n \r\n  \r\n \r\n</xml>\r\n<link rel=\"themeData\r\n\" href=\"file:///C:/Users/ASUS/AppData/Local/Packages/oice_16_974fa576_32c1d314_e43/AC/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_themedata.thmx\" />\r\n<link rel=\"colorSchemeMapping\r\n\" href=\"file:///C:/Users/ASUS/AppData/Local/Packages/oice_16_974fa576_32c1d314_e43/AC/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_colorschememapping.xml\" />\r\n<xml>\r\n \r\n  </xml><p class=\"MsoNormalM\">The International Red Cross and Red Crescent Movement is the world\'s largest\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">humanitarian </span>network, comprising the International Committee of the Red Cross,\r\n191 National Red Cross and Red Crescent Societies, and the <span style=\"font-style: italic;\">International\r\nFederation of Red Cross and Red Crescent Societies</span>. Its central goal is to help\r\nthose who suffer without discrimination and thus contribute to peace in the\r\nworld.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormalM\"><span>The Movement\'s distinctive symbols are the red cross and red crescent\r\nemblems, which serve as protective symbols and express neutrality. These\r\nemblems enable humanitarian workers to work safely in conflict zones, ensuring\r\nthat vital aid reaches those most in need. In 2005, the red crystal emblem was\r\nadopted for countries that do not use the red cross or red crescent emblems for\r\ncultural or political reasons.</span></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<br /></p>', 'en', 5),
(29, 'كيف ساعد العلاج الفيزيائي البطلة الصغيرة ميرا للتغلب على إصابتها بالشلل؟', '<p><br /></p>\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">لا تتابع ميرا (5 أعوام) ألعاب الأولمبياد ونتائجها، بل تنشغل بإنجازها الخاص، النهوض والوقوف بمفردها، وبضع خطوات صغيرة بمساعدة المتطوعين.</p>\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">ميرا ولدت مع شلل دماغي غير تشنّجي، تسبب بشلل في أطرافها الأربعة، وضعف بعضلات الورك، وحرمها من أداء أبسط وظائفها الحركية، لتعتمد كلياً على والدتها.<br />وبعد عدة جلسات علاج فيزيائي منزلية مع متطوعي&nbsp;<span>&nbsp;</span><em style=\" font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\"><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">الهلال الأحمر العربي السوري</strong></em><span>&nbsp;</span>في<span>&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">درعا</span>&nbsp;</span>ركّزت على تقوية عضلات الطرفين السفليين والعلويين والورك، تمكّنت الصغيرة من النهوض والوقوف بالاعتماد على نفسها، ويتابع معها المتطوعون لتمكينها من المشي بشكل متوازن دون مساعدة.</p>\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">والدة ميرا التي تواصلت مع المتطوعين لمساعدة ابنتها تتأمل خطوات طفلتها بسعادة وتأمل أن تتمكن من الوصول للاستقلالية التامة، مع نهاية الجلسات التي تستمر نحو 4 أشهر، وهي جزء من عدة خدمات يقدمها الهلال الأحمر العربي السوري للمصابين وذوي الإعاقة، ومنها أيضاً خدمات تمريضية ومعينات حركية، لتسهيل حياتهم وعونهم للاندماج في مجتمعاتهم، وتخفيف الأعباء عن أسرهم، وذلك بدعم من<span style=\"font-style: italic;\"> الاتحاد الدولي لجمعيات الصليب الأحمر والهلال الأحمر.</span></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<br />', 'ar', 22),
(30, 'Mira isn’t focused on Olympic medals. Instead, she’s writing her own inspiring story', '<p>\r\n\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Five-year-old Mira, born with non-spastic cerebral palsy, faced a world confined to her bed. Paralyzed in all limbs and unable to perform the simplest tasks, she relied entirely on her mother’s care. However, hope emerged with the support of the <span style=\"font-style: italic;\">Syrian Arab Red Crescent.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Mira’s muscles gradually strengthened through dedicated home physical therapy sessions in <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Daraa</span>. With the unwavering support of volunteers, she achieved the incredible milestone of standing on her own two feet. Today, she’s taking her first, determined steps toward independence.</p>\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Mira’s mother watches with joy as her daughter blossoms. The four-month therapy program, which includes nursing care and mobility aids, is part of the Syrian Arab Red Crescent’s comprehensive support for the injured and disabled. With the backing of the <span style=\"font-style: italic;\">IFRC</span>, this vital work empowers individuals like Mira to become active members of their communities.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<br />', 'en', 22),
(31, 'عائلة اسماعيل ترمم خسارات النزوح بمنحة من الهلال الأحمر العربي السوري', '<p>\r\n\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">يرمم اسماعيل تدريجياً خسارات عائلته جراء النزوح من<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">حلب</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>إلى<strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\"><span>&nbsp;</span>السويداء</strong>، بعد افتتاح محل لبيع الأحذية، وكسب قبول السوق سريعاً بفضل خبراته السابقة.</p>\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">الأب الأربعيني غادر مع زوجته وأولاده الأربعة مدينته حلب، تاركاً منزله ومحله لبيع الأحذية، واستقر في منزل للإيجار ببلدة القريا، واضطر للعمل وزوجته بأشغال يومية مؤقتة، لتأمين احتياجات العائلة الكبيرة.</p>\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><em style=\" font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\"><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">“المنحة أعادت لي مهنتي وحياتي”</strong></em><span>&nbsp;</span>يقول اسماعيل الذي تغيرت أحواله، بعد زيارة مركز المجتمعي ببلدة عرى، حيث انضمّ إلى دورة ريادة أعمال، وحصل على منحة ساعدته في افتتاح المحل، بدعمٍ من<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\"><em style=\" font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">المفوضية السامية لشؤون اللاجئين.</em></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">خبرة اسماعيل السابقة ساعدته في كسب قبول السوق كما يقول، وسرعان ما نشطت حركة البيع لديه، وبدأ بتوزيع البضاعة لمحال المنطقة والمناطق المجاورة، وتمكّن من سداد الديون المتراكمة عليه، وتوسيع محله، وإصلاح منزله ليصبح أكثر ملائمة للعيش، وبات أقل قلقاً تجاه احتياجات أسرته.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<br />', 'ar', 23),
(32, 'Ismail’s family rebuilds their lives with a grant', '<p>\r\n\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Ismail, a forty-year-old father, fled<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">Aleppo</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>with his wife and four children, leaving behind their home and shoe store.<br />They settled in a rented house in the town of Al-Qaryain in<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">Sweida</strong>, where he and his wife were forced to work temporary daily jobs to support their large family.</p>\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">After visiting a community center in Ara, Ismail joined an entrepreneurship course and received a grant from the<em style=\" font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\"><span>&nbsp;</span>Syrian Arab Red Crescent</em>, with support from<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\"><em style=\" font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">UNHCR</em></strong>. This grant enabled him to open a shoe store. Drawing on his previous experience, Ismail quickly gained market acceptance and began to rebuild his family’s lives.</p>\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><em style=\" font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\"><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">“The grant gave me my career and my life back,”</strong></em><span>&nbsp;</span>Ismail says.<br />He was able to pay off his accumulated debts, expand his shop, and renovate their house. Ismail’s success also allowed him to distribute his goods to shops in the area and neighboring areas, providing for his family and easing their concerns.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<br />', 'en', 23),
(33, 'يزن يذهب لمدرسته بسهولة ويتمتع بهواياته المفضلة بعد تركيب طرف صناعي', '<p>\r\n\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">لم يكن من السهل على يزن أن يخسر قدمه اليمنى بعمر الثالثة عشر، ويحرم من لعب كرة القدم وركوب الدراجة الهوائية، وأبسط الأنشطة، لكنه اليوم وبعد تركيب طرف اصطناعي والاعتياد عليه، يستطيع التمتع بممارسة هواياته المفضلة، والذهاب إلى المدرسة وقضاء شؤونه بسهولة، الأمر الذي أعاد الفرح للمنزل.</p>\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">فقبل نحو عامين، وفيما يزن يلعب الكرة مع أصدقائه في مبنى متضرر بمنطقة طريق السد في مدينة<strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\"><span>&nbsp;</span>درعا</strong>، سقط عليه جدار وأصيبت قدمه اليمنى إصابة بليغة، أدت إلى البتر، الذي تسبب له ولأسرته بمعاناة كبيرة، حتى علم والده بوجود خدمات يقدمها<span>&nbsp;</span><em style=\" font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\"><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">الهلال الأحمر العربي السوري</strong></em><span>&nbsp;</span>لحالة طفله.</p>\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">وبعد إجراء المتطوعين عدة جلسات<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">علاج فيزيائي</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>في المنزل، لإعادة تأهيل مكان البتر وتحضيره لتركيب الطرف الصناعي، الذي جرى في مركز الأطراف الصناعية التابع للهلال الأحمر العربي السوري في بلدة شبعا ب<strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">ريف دمشق</strong>، مع تدريبه على التعامل معه، ليسهل عليه الحركة والتنقل دون مساعدة.</p>\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">وبعد قرابة عام، استدعى نمو في مكان البتر، استبدال الطرف الصناعي بآخر أكثر ملاءمة، ليعود يزن مجدداً إلى مركز الأطراف الصناعية في شبعا، ويحصل على طرف جديد.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<br />', 'ar', 24),
(34, 'Yazan’s laughter fills his home once more', '<p>\r\n\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">A tragic accident at thirteen stole Yazan’s right foot and the simple joys of playing football with friends.<br />The pain of amputation and the limitations it imposed were a heavy burden for him and his family.<br />However, Yazan’s spirit remained unbroken.</p>\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Hope arrived through the<span>&nbsp;</span><em style=\" font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\"><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">Syrian Arab Red Crescent</strong></em>‘s volunteers. who provided<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">physical therapy</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>at home in<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">Daraa</strong>, preparing Yazan for a prosthetic limb.<br />He received training and support at SARC center in Shebaa in<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">Rural Damascus</strong>, gradually regaining his confidence and mobility.&nbsp; Although growth necessitated a new prosthetic after a year, it was a minor hurdle on his path to a limitless future.</p>\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Today, Yazan walks tall, not just because of his new limb but his unwavering spirit.<br />School is no longer a struggle, but a place of learning and connection.<br />Now he can get back on the field and enjoy activities like he used to, like riding his bike and playing football with his friends.<br /><em style=\" font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">Yazan’s laughter fills his home once more.</em></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<br />', 'en', 24);
