(35, 'العجز يصيب كثيراً من السوريين في رحلتهم لطلب خدمة طبية فكيف يساعدهم الهلال الأحمر العربي السوري؟', '<p>\r\n\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">تتراجع قدرة العائلات في<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">سوريا</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>على الوصول للخدمات الطبية بشكل كبير، إذ شهدت تكاليفها ارتفاعاً كبيراً زاد الهوة بينها وبين دخل الأسر، ومع تضرر أكثر من 40 بالمئة من المؤسسات الصحية جزئياً أو كلياً، تحوّل طلب الرعاية الصحية إلى رحلة شاقة، تضاعف أعباء الأشد ضعفاً، وتدفعهم أحياناً للاستغناء عنها.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">“شعرت بالعجز حينها، فالتكلفة كانت أكبر من استطاعتي بكثير” يقول جميل (48 عاماً) عندما علم أن طفله مصاباً بنقص سمع شديد بالأذنتين ويحتاج إلى سماعتين، لكن عمله بالخياطة لا يغطي كلفتهما الباهظة، فهو بالكاد يوفر مستلزمات أبنائه الأربعة الأساسية، على حد تعبيره.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">الأب راجع مجمع الصاخور الطبي التابع<span>&nbsp;</span><em style=\" font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\"><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">للهلال الأحمر العربي السوري</strong></em><span>&nbsp;</span>في<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">حلب</strong>، وبعد تشخيص حالة الطفل حصل على سماعتين تناسبان شدة نقص السمع لديه، وأصبح معهما قادراً على سماع أصوات أخوته وأمه وأبيه.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">“لم تسعني الفرحة حين رأيت نظرته الأولى نحوي عند سماعه صوتي” يقول الأب الذي كان سيؤجل علاج ابنه إلى أجل غير مسمى.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">وفي ريف<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">اللاذقية</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>تنتظر سلوى (76 عاماً) عيادة الهلال الأحمر المتنقلة التي تزور قريتها القبيسية أسبوعياً، لتراقب مستوى السكر والضغط لديها، وتحصل على أدويتها المزمنة، لكنها اضطرّت لتأجيل عمل جراحي في العين لمدة ستة أشهر، بسبب عدم قدرتها على تأمين كلفته المادية.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">“العيادة تخفف عني أعباء المعاينات والأدوية، وأجور المواصلات، ففي قريتنا لا يوجد منشآت صحية وأقرب مستوصف بعيد جداً” تقول سلوى التي تعمل في الزراعة، وتتحمل مسؤولية عائلة كبيرة، وزوج مصاب ببتر في طرفه السفلي.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">التقديرات الأممية تشير إلى أن 14.9 مليون شخص في سوريا بحاجة مساعدة من أجل الحصول على خدمات صحية منقذة للحياة، فارتفاع تكاليف الطبابة، زاد الضغط على المرافق التي توفر الخدمات بشكل مجاني أو بأسعار رمزية، وجعل مواردها محدودة أمام الطلب الكبير.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">“لا يمكنني الدخول إلى مراكز طبية خاصة فأنا أعمل بأجر يومي لا يكاد يكفي طعامنا وشرابنا” يقول صالح الذي يقطع مسافة 5 كيلومتر للوصول إلى مستوصف الهلال الأحمر في<strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\"><span>&nbsp;</span>الحسكة</strong>، والحصول على خدمات طبية له ولزوجته وأولاده الأربعة.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">ومنذ عام 2011، يزور عبد المتين (88 عاماً) مستوصف للهلال الأحمر في<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">حمص</strong>، حيث يتابع حالته الصحية فهو يعاني من ارتفاع الضغط والسكري ونقص التروية القلبية، ويحصل على أدويته، فراتبه التقاعدي لا يغطي تكلفة زيارة الأطباء والأدوية.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">وتساعد العيادة المتنقلة في مدينة البعث با<strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">لقنيطرة</strong>، أيوب عبد الرزاق (63 عاماً) للحصول على الدواء له ولزوجته التي تعاني من مرض عصبي، ويقول عن خدماتها “تغطي العيادة أكثر من 50% من تكاليف الدواء ولولا وجودها كنا سنضطر للاستغناء عن حاجات المنزل لشراء العلاج”.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">وتزيد المشقة على كبار السن، لصعوبة تنقلهم وعدم توفر دخل لديهم في كثير من الأحيان، ففي قرية العبد بريف دير الزور الشرقي التي لا يتواجد فيها سوى مستوصف لقاحات للأطفال، تنتظر فطوم (80 عاماً) عيادة الهلال الأحمر المتنقلة، لتراقب وضعها الصحي بعد إصابتها بجلطة دماغية ونقص تروية في الدماغ، فيما ساعد الهلال الأحمر حليمة (65 عاماً) التي تعيش وحيدة في السبخة بريف الرقة، في الحصول على عكاز، يعينها الآن على المشي بأمان وتلبية شؤونها.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">وتزيد عوامل كثيرة هشاشة القطاع الصحي في سوريا، من بينها انخفاض الدعم الإنساني، وتدهور الشروط الصحية في المناطق المتضررة وتفشي أمراض معدية كالكوليرا، والزلزال الذي أدى إلى دمار مزيد من المنشآت الصحية وفاقم الظروف الاجتماعية والاقتصادية، وحالات صحية منها سوء التغذية.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">سيلا طفلة ولدت في مدينة دوما ب<strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">ريف</strong><span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">دمشق</strong>، وبعمر 6 أشهر لاحظ والداها أنها تعاني من تأخر بالحركة ونقص شهية وجسم نحيل، وعند مراجعة مستوصف الهلال الأحمر في مدينتهم شخص الأطباء لديها سوء تغذية حاد، وبعد 5 زيارات لعيادة التغذية ومتابعة علاجها بزبدة الفستق والحليب تماثلت للشفاء وتحسنت مؤشرات نموها.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">“اضطررنا للنزوح خمس سنوات، وعدنا بعدها لبيت مدمر كلياً، وزوجي يعاني من مشكلة قلبية وبالكاد يلبي احتياجات أطفالنا الأربعة، ولم يكن بمقدورنا تأمين حليب لابنتي ومكملات غذائية لولا المستوصف” تقول والدة سيلا ويبدو الارتياح على ملامحها لاستقرار حالة طفلتها.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">وفيما الحصول على أبسط خدمات الرعاية الصحية صعباً وشاقاً، يصبح الأمر أكثر تعقيداً مع الخدمات النوعية، وتقول جدة يامن الذي يعاني من شلل دماغي تشنجي أنها كانت تضطر لتأخير جلسات العلاج الفيزيائي لحفيدها حتى تأمين كلفتها الباهظة ما سبب تأخر تطور قدراته، لكنه يتلقى اليوم تلك الجلسات مع فريق العلاج الفيزيائي الجوال التابع للهلال الأحمر العربي السوري.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">يامن (8 سنوات) يعيش مع جدته هو وشقيقته الصغرى بعد وفاة والده، ويستطيع الآن بعد سنتين من المتابعة المشي والوقوف بمفرده، والذهاب إلى المدرسة واللعب مع أصدقائه وودع كرسيه المتحرك.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">فيما تلقت ريماس (12 عاماً) كرسياً متحركاً من الهلال الأحمر لتتمكن من الخروج حيث كانت تضطر للبقاء في غرفتها وقتاً طويلاً كونها تعاني شلل رباعي وتلف في خلايا الدماغ بسبب نقص الأكسجة منذ الولادة، والأب الذي يعمل كموظف براتب محدود لا يستطيع تغطية تكاليف احتياجاتها الكثيرة.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">ووفر الهلال الأحمر العربي السوري خدمات طبية لأكثر من<strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">3.7 &nbsp;مليون</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>شخص في عام 2023، بدعم من شركائه الإنسانيين لتخفيف الأعباء الكبيرة عن الأسر لاسيما الأشد ضعفاً، وضمان حصولهم على<strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\"><span>&nbsp;</span>الرعاية الصحية المنقذة للحياة.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<br />', 'ar', 25),
(36, 'Syrians endure significant challenges while seeking medical care services, how does SARC assist?', '<p>\r\n\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">The Syrian conflict has significantly impacted Syrians’ access to<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">medical care</strong>, with rising costs and damaged infrastructure creating a major burden.<br />This is especially challenging for people with disabilities who often require specialized services.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Fortunately,<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\"><em style=\" font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">the Syrian Arab Red Crescent (SARC)</em></strong><span>&nbsp;</span>helps bridge this gap.<br />Jamil, a father of four, felt helpless when he learned his son needed expensive hearing aids his meager income from tailoring couldn’t afford. However, a visit to the Al-Sakhour Medical Complex, run by SARC in<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">Aleppo</strong>, changed everything.<br />After diagnosis, his son received free hearing aids, allowing him to finally hear his family’s voices.&nbsp; Jamil’s story is just one example of how SARC helps ensure people with disabilities receive the care they need.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Beyond offering basic medical services, SARC provides crucial support for those with specific needs.<br />Yamen’s grandmother, caring for her grandson with cerebral palsy, struggled to afford<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">physical therapy</strong>. Thanks to SARC’s mobile physical therapy team, Yamen can now walk and attend school.&nbsp; Similarly, Rimas, a young girl with quadriplegia, received a wheelchair from SARC, enabling her to leave her room for the first time.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">SARC’s mobile clinics are a lifeline for many Syrians, especially in remote areas.<br />In the countryside of<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">Latakia</strong>, 76-year-old Salwa relies on weekly visits to monitor her blood sugar and blood pressure and obtain chronic medications.<br />The high cost of medical care forces many to make difficult choices, like Saleh, who travels 5 kilometers for his family’s care, or Abdul-Mateen, who depends on SARC for medication since his retirement salary can’t cover doctor visits.&nbsp; The mobile clinic in<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">Quneitra</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>helps Ayoub obtain medicine for his wife’s neurological disease, alleviating a significant financial burden.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">The elderly face particular challenges.&nbsp; Fattoum, 80, in<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">Deir ez-Zor</strong>, waits at the mobile clinic after suffering a stroke, as her village only has a vaccination dispensary.&nbsp; SARC also provided a crutch to Halima, 65, who lives alone in<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">Raqqa</strong>, allowing her to move safely.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">SARC also aids children in need. Sila suffered from malnutrition when she was six months old due to displacement and her family’s limited resources.&nbsp; However, SARC’s nutrition clinic diagnosed and treated her with peanut butter and milk, leading to her recovery.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">UN estimates indicate that 14.9 million people in Syria need assistance to obtain life-saving health services.<br />The crisis has exacerbated the fragility of the health sector, with declining humanitarian support, deteriorating health conditions, outbreaks of infectious diseases, and damage from the earthquake.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">These are just a few examples of the Syrian Arab Red Crescent’s lifesaving work.&nbsp; In 2023 alone,<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">SARC provided medical services to over 3.7 million people.</strong><br />Their interventions offer a glimmer of hope for a healthier future, particularly for Syria’s most vulnerable families.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<br class=\"Apple-interchange-newline\" />\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<br />', 'en', 25);
INSERT INTO `section_details` (`id`, `title`, `content`, `lang`, `section_id`) VALUES
(37, 'مشروع يدعم خطوات الشابات والشباب نحو مستقبل أكثر استقراراً', '<p>\r\n\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><em style=\" font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\"><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">“كانت هناك حاجة كبيرة لترميم البيوت وإصلاح الأدوات الزراعية بعد عودة العائلات”</strong></em><span>&nbsp;</span>لهذا السبب اختار أمير (26 عاماً) مهنة الحدادة بعد عودته من النزوح إلى السلطانية بريف<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">حمص</strong>، واشتغل فيها كعامل لكن دخلها لم يكفه لتعويض خساراته وتأمين احتياجات عائلته الصغيرة.</p>\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><em style=\" font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\"><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">“الأوضاع تغيرت بعدما أصبحت صاحب العمل، لم تعد نهاية الشهر تقلقني، وبإمكاني شراء ما تحتاجه طفلتي متى شئت وبأي وقت “</strong></em><span>&nbsp;</span>يقول أمير عن حاله الآن، وهو من بين 380 شاباً استفاد من مشروع<span>&nbsp;</span><em style=\" font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">الهلال الأحمر العربي السوري</em><span>&nbsp;</span>(نوفو) في<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">حمص</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>بدعم من الصليب الأحمر الدنماركي لدعم الشباب والشابات خلال عامي 2023 و2024.</p>\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">ويهدف المشروع لتطوير مهارات الشباب النفسية والاجتماعية والشخصية والتقنية والكفاءات المتعلقة بريادة الأعمال، ليصبحوا مستعدين للاعتماد على أنفسهم، ومؤهلين للحصول على عمل أو البدء ب<strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">مشاريع صغيرة</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>ومنحهم أدواتها، ومنهم نضال الشاب الذي بدأ العمل في مصبغة بعمر صغير، لكن القلق والتوتر لم يفارقه بسبب الضغوط الاقتصادية وصعوبات معيشية، لتأمين احتياجات أخواته الثلاث ووالديه، وهو معيلهم الوحيد.</p>\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">التدريبات التي انضم لها والمنحة ساعدت نضال (29 عاماً) لشراء ماكينة خياطة وغسالة وبطارية ما أثر بشكل كبير على إنتاجية المصبغة وحسّن دخله، وعن وضعه الجديد يقول<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\"><em style=\" font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">“يمكنني الآن التخطيط لمستقبلي وللزواج أيضاً”</em><span>&nbsp;</span></strong>ويخبرنا بسعادة عن حلمه بتطوير مهنته وافتتاح فروع بكل مناطق حمص.</p>\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">عبد القادر (33 عاماً) حقق حلمه أيضاً وأصبح<span>&nbsp;</span><em style=\" font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\"><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">“شريكاً في المكان الذي كان فيه مجرد عامل بسيط”</strong></em><span>&nbsp;</span>على حد تعبيره، فالتدريبات مكّنته من فهم الفرص المتاحة، والتفكير بمشاريع قابلة للتطبيق ودراسة الجدوى الاقتصادية منها، الأمر الذي ساعده في البدء بمشروع ماكينة قص ليزر في منطقة العرقوب بـ<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">حلب</strong>.</p>\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">وبعد أن كان الأجر اليومي الذي يتلقاه كعامل لا يكفي تأمين احتياجات طفليه وزوجته، أصبح الآن صاحب مشروع ويخطط لزيادة رأس ماله لتصنيع منتجات جديدة، وهو واحد من 362 شخصاً استفادوا من المشروع بحلب.</p>\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">هبة الله (33 عاماً) كانت من بين المستفيدين من المشروع أيضاً، الذي ساعدها في افتتاح معهد ينفذ دورات منها حساب ذهني وروبيك في صلاح الدين بـ<strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\"><span>&nbsp;</span>حلب</strong>.</p>\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><em style=\" font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\"><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">“تغير كل شيء، كنت أشعر أن جهدي ضائع، ولا أجد فرص عمل تناسب مهاراتي، لكن تدريبات ريادة الأعمال دفعتني للتفكير بعقلية مختلفة، وشجعتني للبدء بمشروعي الخاص”</strong></em><span>&nbsp;</span>تقول هبة الله وهي أم لطفلين.</p>\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">المعهد منح الأم الثلاثينية دخلاً ثابتاً نسبياً يغطي احتياجات أطفالها دون مساعدة أحد أو الاضطرار للاستدانة كما تقول.</p>\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">ويساعد مشروع نوفو بترميم ما تسببت به الأزمة في سورية من خسارة الشباب والشابات لفرص تعلّم وتدريب كثيرة، وتلقي مهارات تعينهم لدخول سوق العمل، أو امتلاك مشاريع خاصة، في وقت تزداد فيه الحاجة لدورهم الحيوي من أجل بناء السلام ومجتمع أكثر استدامة.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<br />', 'ar', 26),
(38, 'The Syrian Arab Red Crescent (Novo) Project Empowers Young Syrians', '<p>\r\n\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><em style=\" font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">The Novo Project addresses a critical need: helping families rebuild their lives after displacement.</em><br />Many young people, like Amir (26), faced difficulties upon returning to their homes in Al-Sultaniyah, rural<strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\"><span>&nbsp;</span>Homs</strong>. With limited job opportunities, supporting his family was a challenge.</p>\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><em style=\" font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\"><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">“Renovating homes and repairing tools was crucial,”</strong></em><span>&nbsp;</span>Amir explains.<br />Previously a laborer, his income fell short.</p>\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">The Novo Project, supported by the Danish Red Cross in 2023-2024, intervened.<br />It equips young men and women with vital skills: psychological, social, personal, and technical expertise related to entrepreneurship.</p>\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Amir is one of 380 beneficiaries in Homs. Now a business owner, he proudly states,<span>&nbsp;</span><em style=\" font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\"><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">“Month-end anxieties are gone. I can provide for my family whenever needed.”</strong></em></p>\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Nidal (29) exemplifies another success story.<br />Working in the laundry since his youth, financial pressures and the burden of supporting his parents and sisters caused him constant anxiety.</p>\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">The project’s training and scholarship program was a turning point. Nidal used the funds to purchase a sewing machine, washing machine, and battery.<br /><em style=\" font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\"><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">“Production soared, and my income improved significantly,”</strong><span>&nbsp;</span></em>he shares.</p>\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><em style=\" font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\"><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">“Now, I can even plan for the future and marriage!”</strong></em>&nbsp; His dream: expanding his laundry business across Homs.</p>\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Similar success stories unfold in<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">Aleppo</strong>. Abdul Qader (33) rose from<em style=\" font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\"><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\"><span>&nbsp;</span>“a simple worker”</strong></em><span>&nbsp;</span>to a partner in his workplace.<br />The training program honed his business acumen, allowing him to launch a laser-cutting machine project in Arqoub.<br />His plans include expanding capital and product lines.&nbsp; He’s one of 362 beneficiaries in Aleppo.</p>\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Hiba (33) also found a new purpose.&nbsp; This mother of two struggled to find suitable employment.<br /><em style=\" font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\"><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">“It felt like a wasted effort,”</strong></em><span>&nbsp;</span>she recalls.<br />The Novo Project’s entrepreneurship training ignited a shift in mindset, encouraging her to start an institute offering mental arithmetic and Rubik’s Cube courses in Salah al-Din, Aleppo.</p>\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><em style=\" font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\"><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">“Everything changed,”</strong></em><span>&nbsp;</span>Hebat Allah says.<br /><em style=\" font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\"><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">“The institute provides a stable income, allowing me to support my children without relying on others or debt.”</strong></em></p>\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">The Novo Project bridges the gap created by the Syrian crisis, offering young people the skills they need to enter the workforce or establish their businesses.<br />As Syria rebuilds, their contributions are vital for a more peaceful and sustainable future.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<br />', 'en', 26);
