(39, 'سوريا بعد عام من الزلزال … تعاف مؤجل والمحتاجون في ازدياد', '<p>\r\n\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">الوجوه المتعبة والبيوت المتصدّعة والركام، تخبر كلها أن الكارثة لم تغادر الكثير من البلدات والمدن في سوريا، بل<span>&nbsp;</span><em style=\" font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\"><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">“تزداد الحياة فيها صعوبة كل يوم”</strong></em><span>&nbsp;</span>كما يقول يعرب الذي يسكن غرفة مسبقة الصنع بجبلة، في ريف<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">اللاذقية</strong>، بعد انهيار بيته في الزلزال.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">يعرب يصف نفسه بالمحظوظ كونه نجا من موت محتم، لكنه بات دون عمل يعيل به أسرته واحتياجات والديه خاصة الأدوية التي ارتفع ثمنها كثيراً على حد تعبيره.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">عام كامل مرّ على الزلزال الذي ضرب سوريا</strong>، لكن عائلات كثيرة لا تزال عالقة في ذلك اليوم الكارثي، لم تخطو خطوة واحدة نحو التعافي، فالأزمات الإنسانية والاقتصادية المتلاحقة وتأثير التغيّر المناخي، جرّدها من كل قدراتها على التكيّف أو المواجهة.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">“ليس لدي القدرة على الترميم أو استئجار منزل”</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>بهذا يجيب محمد ديوب كل من يسأله عن سبب عدم مغادرة بيته المتصدّع في ريف اللاذقية، ومياه الأمطار المتسربة من السقف المتشقق، تنذر بخطر سقوطه فيما لو اشتد الطقس قليلاً.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">محمد واحد من 8 مليون شخص تأثروا بزلزال<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">6 شباط</strong>، ولا يدل الرقم على شدته فقط، بل أيضاً على البنى التحتية الهشّة للمناطق التي ضربها، وضعف المجتمعات التي تستقبل آلاف العائلات النازحة، فكانت دقائق قليلة كفيلة بأن تعيد محاولاتهم للتعافي إلى نقطة الصفر.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><em style=\" font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\"><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">“أصبح احتمال عودتنا شبه مستحيل ومن لم يتضرر بالحرب تضرر بالزلزال”</strong></em><span>&nbsp;</span>يقول أبو محمد (اسم مستعار) الذي نزح إلى الرمل الجنوبي في اللاذقية من جسر الشغور بإدلب، بحثاً عن الأمان، لكنه مع الأزمات المتتالية، فقد مدخراته، وكل ما يملك، ولا يكاد مدخوله اليوم يغطي الطعام والشراب، وسنواته الستون لم تعد تسمح بأي خطوة جديدة سوى الاجتماع مع صديقه النازح من<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">حلب</strong>، أمام البحر وتبادل الهموم.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><em style=\" font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\"><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">الهلال الأحمر العربي السوري</strong></em><span>&nbsp;</span>استجاب منذ اللحظات الأولى لوقوع الزلزال الذي أدى لوفاة وإصابة نحو<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">17 ألف</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>شخص، وتشريد الآلاف، ودمار وتضرر<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">123,226</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>مبنى، وحاول متطوعوه بأقصى طاقاتهم تخفيف آثاره عن المنكوبين، من المساعدة في إنقاذ الضحايا، إلى الرعاية الإسعافية والصحية، والعلاج الفيزيائي، وخدمات الإيواء والإغاثة، والدعم النفسي والقانوني، وترميم الخدمات الحيوية، والمساعدة النقدية ودعم سبل العيش، والتي تخطت بمجملها الـ<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">23.5</strong><span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">مليون خدمة إنسانية</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">لكن الاحتياجات كانت كبيرة، فالكارثة حلّت على مجتمع يحتاج فيه<strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\"><span>&nbsp;</span>15.3</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>مليون شخص للمساعدة من أجل تأمين أبسط احتياجاتهم، العدد الذي ارتفع إلى 16.7 مليون شخص في عام 2024، وبلد 90 بالمئة من سكانه تحت خط الفقر.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><em style=\" font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\"><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">“كنت أريد ترميم المنزل بالمبلغ، لكن ابنتي أصيبت بالتهاب رئة تطلب دخولها المشفى والكثير من الأدوية، فصرفت معظمه على علاجها”</strong></em><span>&nbsp;</span>تقول ديمة<br />وهي من المتضررين الذين حصلوا على مساعدة نقدية من<span>&nbsp;</span><em style=\" font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">الهلال الأحمر العربي السوري</em><span>&nbsp;</span>لترميم تشققات جدران منزلها بحلب، وشراء ألبسة شتوية لصغارها، وبعض احتياجات المنزل.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">ديمة المعيلة لثلاثة أطفال أكبرهم بسن الخامسة، أعادت ترتيب أولوياتها بسبب مرض بناتها المتكرر بالتهاب الرئة، وطول مدة شفائهن، ربما بسبب تلوث الهواء بنواتج احتراق الحطب الذي تستخدمه للتدفئة، وأجلّت فكرة ترميم الجدران إلى أجل غير مسمى.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">الاحتياجات المعيشية الكبيرة جعلت الاهتمام بال<strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">صحة النفسية</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>أمر ثانوي للكثير من المتضررين رغم أهميتها، وتقول إحدى متطوعات الهلال الأحمر العربي السوري العاملة في هذا المجال، أن عدم تحسن أحوال العائلات بعد عام على الزلزال، واضطرار الكثير منهم للسكن عند أقربائهم وطلب المساعدة، زادت شدتهم النفسية، وبات من الصعب عليهم تخطي حالات الصدمة والقلق والاكتئاب وغيرها من الاضطرابات التي زادت بشكل كبير.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">وما يخيف السوريون اليوم حقاً فقدان الأمل، مع تدهور الأحوال الاقتصادية، وتضاعف تكاليف المعيشة، ونقص تمويل المساعدات الإنسانية، الذي أصبح أثره واضحاً، الأمر الذي يتركهم في مواجهة<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">مستقبل مجهول</strong>، ويجعلهم فريسة سهلة لأي أزمة مهما كانت بسيطة.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<br />\r\n\r\n\r\n<p><br /></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><video-container style=\"display: inline-block;\"><iframe rte-for=\"insertvideo\" border=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\" data-url=\"https://www.facebook.com/share/v/1y5oMMDBHz/\" src=\"https://www.facebook.com/share/v/1y5oMMDBHz/\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 475px; height: 267px;\"></iframe></video-container></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p><br /></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><video-container style=\"display: inline-block;\"><iframe rte-for=\"insertvideo\" border=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\" data-url=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mGPoz6bjaK8\" src=\"https://youtube.com/embed/mGPoz6bjaK8?wmode=opaque\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 640px; height: 360px;\"></iframe></video-container></div>', 'ar', 27),
(40, 'One-year marks since Syria earthquake', '<p>\r\n\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">The effects of the disaster, which never went away, are evident in the worn-out faces and cracked houses in Syrian towns and cities, but as Yaroub, who now lives in a prefabricated room in Jableh in the countryside of<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">Latakia</strong>, puts it,<span>&nbsp;</span><em style=\" font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\"><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">“life gets harder.”</strong></em><span>&nbsp;</span>His house collapsed due to an<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">earthquake</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Yaroub considers himself fortunate to have survived a certain death, but he is currently unable to support his family financially, particularly concerning his parents’ increasing medical expenses.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">A year has passed since the<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">earthquake</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>struck, and many families are still living through the horrific day.<br />They failed to move past it or make even a small step in the direction of recovery, which led to a lack of adaptation and resistance, which in turn caused further problems, including the<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">economic</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>and<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">humanitarian</strong><span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">crises</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>as well as<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">climate change</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When asked why he doesn’t leave his cracked house in the countryside of Latakia,<br />Mohamed Dayoub responds,<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\"><em style=\" font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">“I cannot rent or restore a house.”</em></strong><span>&nbsp;</span>If the weather worsens, there is a serious risk of rain seeping through the crannied ceiling.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Mohamed is just one of the 8&nbsp;million people&nbsp;affected&nbsp;by the<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">February 6 earthquake</strong>. This figure highlights the size of the disaster, the brittleness of the areas it hit, and the vulnerability of the communities hosting the thousands of displaced families. It only took a few minutes for their attempts to recover to fall apart.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">After being forced to flee Jisr al-Shughur in<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">Idlib</strong>,Abu Mohamed (a pseudonym) says,<em style=\" font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\"><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\"><span>&nbsp;</span>“The possibility of our return has become almost impossible, and whoever was not harmed by the crisis was harmed by the earthquake.”</strong></em><br />But as the financial crises continued, he lost everything he owned, including his savings, and barely his salary pays for food and drink. At sixty years old, he is too old to take any further action beyond meeting his friend, who was uprooted from<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">Aleppo</strong>, by the sea, and sharing worries.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">From the first moments of the earthquake, which resulted in approximately<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">17,000 deaths</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>and injuries, thousands of displaced people, and the destruction or damage of<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">123,226 buildings</strong>, the<span>&nbsp;</span><em style=\" font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\"><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">Syrian Arab Red Crescent</strong></em><span>&nbsp;</span>acted. Volunteers made every effort to lessen the impact on those affected, from aiding in victim rescue to offering emergency medical attention and physical therapy.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Over<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">23.5</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>million humanitarian services were provided, including cash assistance, livelihood support, psychological and legal support, shelter and relief services, and the rehabilitation&nbsp;of vital&nbsp;services.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">However, there were enormous needs because the disaster struck a society&nbsp;where<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">90% of people live below the poverty line</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>and where 15.3 million people needed assistance to meet their most basic needs.<br />By 2024, that number had increased to<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">16.7</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>million people.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\"><em style=\" font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">“My daughter had pneumonia and needed hospitalization and a lot of medication, so I spent most of it on her treatment,”</em></strong><span>&nbsp;</span>says Dima,<br />one of those affected who received financial aid from the<span>&nbsp;</span><em style=\" font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">Syrian Arab Red Crescent</em><span>&nbsp;</span>to fix wall cracks in her house in<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">Aleppo</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>and purchase winter clothing for her kids. and a few necessities for the home.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">The mother, the sole breadwinner to three children (the eldest is five years old), rearranged her priorities when her daughters fell ill frequently. It was suspected that the pollution from burning firewood for warmth was the source of the illnesses.<br />She delayed the idea of restoring her cracked house for anonymous timing.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Despite the significance of mental health, many impacted have found that it is secondary to their basic needs.<br /><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">A year after the earthquake</strong>, according to one of the<span>&nbsp;</span><em style=\" font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">Syrian Arab Red Crescent</em><span>&nbsp;</span>volunteers working in psychological support, the families’ circumstances have not improved, and many of them were forced to live with their relatives and seek assistance, which has increased their psychological distress.<br />They are having a harder time overcoming cases of shock, anxiety, depression, and other disorders, which have increased significantly.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">What truly frightens Syrians today is the<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">loss of hope</strong>, with the deterioration of economic conditions, the doubled cost of living, and the inadequate funding for humanitarian aid.<br />Their future is<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">uncertain</strong>, and they are therefore vulnerable to any crisis, no matter how minor.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p><br /></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><video-container style=\"display: inline-block;\"><iframe rte-for=\"insertvideo\" border=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\" data-url=\"https://www.facebook.com/share/v/1y5oMMDBHz/\" src=\"https://www.facebook.com/share/v/1y5oMMDBHz/\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 484px; height: 272px;\"></iframe></video-container></div>', 'en', 27),
