tical-align: baseline\">Damascus</u></strong><span>&nbsp;</span>– Abou Remmaneh.</p><p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Any resume without<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\"><u style=\" font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">Subject</u></strong><span>&nbsp;</span>will be automatically rejected.</p><p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">Only short-listed candidates will be contacted.</strong></p><p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><u style=\" font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">Incomplete file or application in a language other than English will be rejected</u></p><p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">Purpose:</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>the community services programme started in SARC since 2006 supporting SARC in their humanitarian activities, where the operation has been growing enormously since the outbreak of the Syrian crisis.</p><p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">With multiple donors and increased funding there is a demand for improved and more detailed reporting, assessment and follow-up to ensure accountability and transparency to secure continues donor support in the future.</p><p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">Tasks:<span>&nbsp;</span></strong>The tasks should include but not necessarily be limited to:</p><p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">Support to the Community services&nbsp; &amp; protection Unit</strong></p><ul style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 2.14286em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: square; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><li style=\" margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">Prepare and manage contracts for staff and volunteers at HQ and in the Community Centres and Mobile Teams etc. including leave, holiday and warnings according to SARC procedures</li><li style=\" margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">Provide logistical and administrative support in planning and conduction of trainings, meetings, regional visits, field trips etc., including correspondence by email or fax to branches, hotel bookings, travel arrangements, material procurement etc.</li><li style=\" margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">Participate in trainings when required</li><li style=\" margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">Manage database of registered beneficiaries. Collect data from community centres, and compile of statistics for reports, etc.</li><li style=\" margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">Verify that data from the field is aligned with Concord reports. Validate correct data.</li><li style=\" margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">Support the community services Project Coordinator and community services Finance Administrator in translation, preparation of memos, and communication to the Community centres, volunteers etc. as required</li><li style=\" margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">Undertake regular field trips to the social centres to monitor and support Community Centre Coordinators in administrative procedures.</li><li style=\" margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">Ensure office supplies are replenished and/or purchase as required. Maintain office equipment in Community Centre/Mobile Teams and ensure regular service checks and repairs</li><li style=\" margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">Maintain filing system for the Community Services Unit</li><li style=\" margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">Maintain fixed asset lists for Community centres/Mobile Teams</li><li style=\" margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">Support the procurement process for CS when required</li><li style=\" margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">Report promptly on any administrative irregularities encountered to the Community services manager</li><li style=\" margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">Any other task relevant to the projects as assigned by the Community services manager</li></ul><p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">Terms of employment:</strong></p><ul style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 2.14286em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: square; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><li style=\" margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">Employment is full time according to SARC guidelines</li><li style=\" margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">Salary scale, gratuities, leave, etc., are according to the SARC guidelines for the level.</li></ul><p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.25em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong style=\" font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline\">Qualifications:</strong></p><ul style=\" margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 2.14286em; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tajawal, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: square; col